        content: '<div class="bloc1"><p>What is a blockchain?</p></div><div class="bloc2"><img src="https://s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/c8c73987-3c95-40b6-93c8-a9f347b230c6/Instructor_-_Medium.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=AKIAT73L2G45EIPT3X45%2F20230703%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20230703T180818Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Signature=073162f47a6e16f61f49654f61ad33a7afbff139b6398737a9d6737744a94fdd&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-id=GetObject"></div>'
